This Service is built using ASP.Net Core 2.0

Run Docker-Compose file in project root directory to Build the project and publish the artifacts to a working directory and then create an images using those build artifacts.

Use "Docker-Compose build" to build the project and then create the image.

Use "Docker-Compose up" to start the containers.

API is exposed using port 5000, port numbers are specified in Docker-Compose file. Ports can be changed to meet any requirements. 

File are not persisted in this project. But we can persist them by mounting the network drives/shares to container from dockerfile. 

File expiration dates are stored into expiration.JSON file, And if the file with same name is uploaded second time expiration date will update too. 